# MediFlow AI вҖ” Implementation Plan

## Overview

**MediFlow AI** is an AI-first CRM for pharmaceutical field representatives to manage interactions with Healthcare Professionals (HCPs). The system features a **LangGraph agent with 6 tools**, dual-mode interaction logging (structured form + conversational AI chat), a dashboard, analytics, rich timeline history, and compliance monitoring вҖ” all powered by **Groq's gemma2-9b-it**.

---

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend ["Frontend вҖ” React + Redux"]
        Dashboard["рҹ“Ҡ Dashboard"]
        LogPage["рҹ“қ Log Interaction"]
        FormMode["Structured Form"]
        ChatMode["AI Chat + Voice"]
        Timeline["рҹ“… Interaction Timeline"]
        Analytics["рҹ“Ҳ Analytics"]
        Search["рҹ”Қ Global Search"]
    end

    subgraph Auth ["Authentication"]
        JWT["JWT Token Auth"]
        Login["Login Page"]
    end

    subgraph Backend ["Backend вҖ” FastAPI"]
        API["REST API + CORS"]
        AuthMW["Auth Middleware"]
        Agent["LangGraph Agent"]
        Pipeline["AI Processing Pipeline"]
    end

    subgraph Tools ["LangGraph Tools (6)"]
        T1["рҹ”§ Log Interaction"]
        T2["рҹ”§ Edit Interaction"]
        T3["рҹ”§ Lookup HCP"]
        T4["рҹ”§ Next Best Action"]
        T5["рҹ”§ Interaction History"]
        T6["рҹ”§ Compliance Checker"]
    end

    subgraph DB ["PostgreSQL"]
        Users["users"]
        HCPs["hcps"]
        Interactions["interactions"]
        Products["products"]
        FollowUps["follow_ups"]
        Notifications["notifications"]
        AuditLogs["audit_logs"]
        Sessions["chat_sessions"]
    end

    Login --> JWT --> AuthMW
    Frontend --> API
    API --> AuthMW --> Agent
    Agent --> Pipeline
    Pipeline --> Tools
    Tools --> DB
```

---

## AI Processing Pipeline

Every user message through the chat interface passes through this pipeline inside the LangGraph agent:

```mermaid
graph LR
    A["User Message"] --> B["Intent Detection"]
    B --> C["Entity Extraction"]
    C --> D["Sentiment Analysis"]
    D --> E["Compliance Check"]
    E --> F["Summary Generation"]
    F --> G["Recommendation Engine"]
    G --> H["Tool Execution"]
    H --> I["Confidence Scoring"]
    I --> J["Response + Store"]
```

This pipeline is embedded in the agent's system prompt and tool logic вҖ” the LLM handles intent/entity/sentiment naturally, and tools handle storage and compliance.

